  <summary date="2016-04-20T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Flexibility in Electronic Health Record Reporting Act 

This bill&#160;requires the Department&#160;of Health and Human Services, with respect to electronic health record (EHR) meaningful use incentive programs under Medicare and Medicaid, to continue through 2016 to allow the use of quarterly reporting without regard to the payment year or the stage of meaningful use criteria involved.</summary>
